        {
            "title": "中國秦發折讓10%配股籌3.16億元",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國秦發(00866)公布，於今早開市前訂立配售協議，以先舊後新方式配股集資約3.16億元；配股價3.51元，較該股昨天收市價3.9元折讓10%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：中國秦發官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00866.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：中國秦發官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/20240626_FI_source-web_00866.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：中國秦發官網</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">若以該股前5個交易日平均收市價3.744元比較，配股價較之折讓約6.25%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">集資所得淨額約3.1億元，其中約46%用於公司在印尼礦山的建設及開發；約23%用於採礦設備；約21%用於標宇建設、約10%用於承包及其他雜項開支，以支持印尼礦山的開發。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708119-%e4%b8%ad%e5%9c%8b%e7%a7%a6%e7%99%bc%e6%8a%98%e8%ae%9310%e9%85%8d%e8%82%a1%e7%b1%8c3-16%e5%84%84%e5%85%83",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/06/00866-Web.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 08:43:04",
