            "title": "黑期夜期齊高水逾280點 滙控ADR反彈4.2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">新加坡黑期於今早約8時11分升416點或1.65%，報25635點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">港股ADR指數報25497點，較香港上日現貨收市高247點或0.98%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股1.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">騰訊(00700)ADR收市折合每股港幣509.1元，較上日香港收市高3.06元或0.6%；阿里巴巴(09988)ADR收市折合每股港幣130.2元，較上日香港收市高0.3元或0.23%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">美團(03690)ADR收市折合每股港幣75.8元，較上日香港收市高0.38元或0.5%；京東(09618)ADR收市折合每股港幣99.3元，較上日香港收市高1.26元或1.29%；小米(01810)ADR收市折合每股港幣32.7元，較上日香港收市高0.67元或2.1%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：騰訊官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/bplib_20230703-101229__source-web_00700.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：騰訊官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滙控(00005)ADR收市折合每股港幣136.3元，較上日香港收市高5.5元或4.2%；友邦(01299)ADR收市折合每股港幣82.2元，較上日香港收市高1.18元或1.46%；港交所(00388)ADR收市折合每股港幣410.5元，較上日香港收市高5.7元或1.41%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"圖片來源：滙控官網\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2024/04/20230829_FI_source-web_HSBC-sign-Paris.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">圖片來源：滙控官網</p>\n</a>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中國平安(02318)ADR收市折合每股港幣65.5元，較上日香港收市高0.91元或1.41%；建設銀行(00939)ADR收市折合每股港幣7.8元，較上日香港收市高0.04元或0.49%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒指期貨夜市收報25534點，升402點，較上日恒指收市25249點，高水285點。科指期貨夜市收報4900點，較上日科指收市高水70點；國指期貨夜市收報8585點，較上日國指收市高水101點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708051-%e9%bb%91%e6%9c%9f%e5%a4%9c%e6%9c%9f%e9%bd%8a%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b4%e9%80%be280%e9%bb%9e-%e6%bb%99%e6%8e%a7adr%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%884-2",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/02/ADR-1_source-bp_-2-1.png.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-05 08:17:18",
            "source": "bastillepost",
            "kind": 2,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "日韓股市大幅高開 日股暫回升約2000點 韓股彈近10%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">日韓等亞洲主要股市經歷近日小股災後，今早終於跟隨隔晚歐美股市反彈，日股與韓股今早均大幅高開。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/08/202508013_FI_source-ap_South_Korea_Financial_Markets.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">截至香港時間上午約8時09分，日經平均指數報56319點，升2074點或3.82%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">南韓首爾綜合指數暫報5585點，反彈492點或9.66%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15708033-%e6%97%a5%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%b8%82%e5%a4%a7%e5%b9%85%e9%ab%98%e9%96%8b-%e6%97%a5%e8%82%a1%e6%9a%ab%e5%9b%9e%e5%8d%87%e7%b4%842000%e9%bb%9e-%e9%9f%93%e8%82%a1%e5%bd%88%e8%bf%9110",
